remarks.para:
Use before iterating over a collection to batch-load all snapshots upfront:
- prefetch_snapshots: resource_type: character resource_ids: ${participants | map('id')} filter: - character-personality
- foreach: variable: p collection: ${participants} do: - load_snapshot: # Cache hit - instant name: char resource_type: character resource_id: ${p.id}

